## CSS Architecture
- Single stylesheet: `assets/styles.css`
- CSS variables in `:root` — always use these, never hardcode colors
- `--headerH: 128px` — used by `#siteHeader` height and `.hero` calc
- Logo: `.site-logo` at `100px` desktop, scales down at breakpoints
- Page cards: `.page` class with `margin-top: 8px`
- Cards: `.card` and `a.card` (clickable version with hover)
- `.notice-card` — yellow bordered card for warnings (check-in page)
- Breakpoints: 760px (2-col grid), 900px (mobile header), 640px, 420px

## JavaScript Architecture
- Single file: `assets/site.js`
- Self-contained, no dependencies
- Functions: `injectHeader()`, `setupMenu()`, `applyHeaderTheme()`, `setupScrollTheme()`, `applyHeroImage()`, `loadWeather()`, `loadGA4()`
- All image/nav paths must use **absolute paths** (e.g. `/images/Paradise.png`)
- `isGuest` flag — `window.location.pathname.includes('/guest/')` controls menu and logo link
- Guest menu includes full guest navigation + divider + Plan Your Stay, Paradise Info, Paradise Home
- Public menu includes Home, Paradise Info, Plan Your Stay, Sign Up — Stay in the Loop, Book Now
- Weather auto-refreshes every 5 minutes via `setTimeout`
- Hero image swaps day/night at hour 7 (7am) and hour 19 (7pm)

